Code preview of the table C_展位属性历史信息表

alter table "C_BoothAttributeHistory"
drop constraint FK_C_BAH_2_C_BOOTH_PK;

drop table "C_BoothAttributeHistory" cascade constraints;

/*==============================================================*/
/* Table: "C_BoothAttributeHistory" */
/*==============================================================*/
create table "C_BoothAttributeHistory"
(
"HistoryID" NUMBER(32) not null,
"FloorID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothID" NUMBER(32),
"BoothCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"AttributeCode" VARCHAR2(20),
"AttributeName" NVARCHAR2(100),
"AttributeValue" NVARCHAR2(100),
"StartTime" TIMESTAMP,
"EndTime" TIMESTAMP,
"Enable" INTEGER,
"CreateBy" NUMBER(32),
"CreateTime" TIMESTAMP,
constraint PK_C_BOOTHATTRIBUTEHISTORY primary key ("HistoryID")
);

comment on column "C_BoothAttributeHistory"."AttributeCode" is
'A01:一级分类
A02:展位等级
A03:实测面积
A04:公摊系数
A05:预算单价
A06:空间信息
A07:图纸面积

';

comment on column "C_BoothAttributeHistory"."Enable" is
'1：启用
0：停用';

alter table "C_BoothAttributeHistory"
add constraint FK_C_BAH_2_C_BOOTH_PK foreign key ("BoothID")
references "C_Booth" ("BoothID");
